# API Design Workshop - Designer agent

NAME api-designer

INPUT task

GOAL design """
Design a RESTful API specification for: $task
Include: resource naming, endpoints with HTTP methods/paths/schemas,
status codes for success and error, authentication approach,
pagination strategy, rate limiting headers.
Output as OpenAPI 3.0 YAML.
Prioritize consistency and developer ergonomics over cleverness.
""" -> api_spec

RUN main USING design
